  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine 2% chlorhexidine wipes are effective in preventing
      of colonization of multi-drug resistant bacteria in intensive care unit patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the usefulness of bathing with chlorhexidine wipe to
      reduce the risks of multidrug resistant bacteria acquisition and hospital-acquired
      bloodstream infection among ICU patients
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
